Inkjet Technology


                    We offer innovative inkjet technologies and printing inks for commercial and desktop markets.
                
Quality manufacturing, extensive technical expertise, and strong research and development positions our inkjet business to help customers overcome the challenges of current and emerging inkjet printing applications. Our inkjet colorants and inks use a unique and proprietary stabilization technique, providing superior stability and a high level of formulation flexibility. Additionally, our CAB-O-JET® pigment dispersions enable ink formulators to solve unique challenges within the commercial, desktop, office and consumer markets.



